Revelation 21 verse 4 promises.

00:07:43.769 --> 00:07:49.769
And tea will wipe out every tear from their eyes, and death will be no more.

00:07:49.769 --> 00:07:53.769
Neither will morning nor outcry, nor pain be any more.

00:07:53.769 --> 00:07:56.769
The former things have passed away.

